Fat snail meat are a type of food that can be obtained by cooking fat snails on a fire or cooking range, requiring level 22 Cooking and granting 95 experience when successful. Players may burn the snail while cooking one, resulting in a burnt snail; the burn rate while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels. It will stop burning entirely at Cooking level 56 on both ranges and fires.

Fat snail meat heals 7-9 Hitpoints.
